st: explain that fork PRs are not supported in v1\n- metadata ref missing: say no Agent Trail metadata was found for this public PR\n- metadata found but no matching sessions: say metadata exists, but no related\n  agent sessions matched the PR review target or head branch\n- weak branch-only matches: show them separately as possible evidence\n- fetch/read error: show a retryable error without implying no agent work exists\n- metadata too large or malformed: show that metadata was found but could not be\n","tool_name":null,"tool_input":null,"source_record":{"timestamp":"2026-05-24T15:12:26.346Z","type":"response_item","payload":{"type":"function_call_output","call_id":"[REDACTED:entropy]"}}}